    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>story</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/df535eb2eac59c8e4bc2e9c7b33b2722.poster.avif?t=1764237231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/df535eb2eac59c8e4bc2e9c7b33b2722.webm?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/df535eb2eac59c8e4bc2e9c7b33b2722.mp4?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Someone was interested in multiple flickering incidents spanning time and place. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>He traced it to a single photograph purportedly showing a single fairy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Begin Your Exploration</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/2653a6eab6a5942b487586edbbfb1d88.poster.avif?t=1764237231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/2653a6eab6a5942b487586edbbfb1d88.webm?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/2653a6eab6a5942b487586edbbfb1d88.mp4?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/8cf45bb5375ffdb9b7109808b91ded81.poster.avif?t=1764237231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/8cf45bb5375ffdb9b7109808b91ded81.webm?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/8cf45bb5375ffdb9b7109808b91ded81.mp4?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Items scattered here and there are important to the story of the game there. In this game, items are not only to be retrieved. Swallowing and &quot;exhaling&quot; blood is one of the most important elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The &quot;exsanguination&quot; element is the ability to take the item into the body and gradually gain abilities that are crucial to the story, but at the same time it drains and slows down the player's physical strength. However, in this game, the physical strength gauge (HP) is never directly related to survival (game completion). It has a completely different meaning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something&quot; is coming at you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a player swallows an item and &quot;vomits (bleeds) blood,&quot; &quot;something&quot; smells the player's blood and comes after the player. The &quot;something&quot; will transform itself by obtaining blood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the &quot;something&quot; catches you, you will be eliminated from the game immediately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the right player for this story and reach the goal while giving blood to the &quot;something&quot;, while being weak and hiding from it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Something is approaching…</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/79258d221fefe9806cf8ed95f3627ba3.poster.avif?t=1764237231\" width=676 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/79258d221fefe9806cf8ed95f3627ba3.webm?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338670/extras/79258d221fefe9806cf8ed95f3627ba3.mp4?t=1764237231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>This is a VR horror game.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two types of locomotion are available: smooth movement using the joystick and teleportation (coming soon).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose smooth movement for a more immersive experience, or teleportation if you prefer to reduce motion sickness.</p>",
